----------

* `OpenTelemetry Jaeger Exporter <https://opentelemetry-python.readthedocs.io/en/latest/exporter/jaeger/jaeger.html>`_
* `Jaeger <https://www.jaegertracing.io/>`_
* `OpenTelemetry Project <https://opentelemetry.io/>`_
